uote><blockquote>你去邊檔解籤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去雲姑 <br />\n解愛情 仲等緊準唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係雲姑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求左咩簽?<br />\n我之前都求左枝下下... 心諗以為死得 但雲姑都講到仲有機會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係等緊準唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊等邊充實自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ff9e889643df1eef34a762199fad9bac856b32","tid":474333,"uid":16594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:40:44.000Z","msg":"Btw... 你信黃大仙個結果定雲姑果套? <br />\n我覺得黃大仙係話你知個結果 而雲姑個角色係幫助你可以更好或者個結果無咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似講到1999"},{"pid":"0169c188c254d932b4e04b7956a0d1a1b25d059c","tid":474333,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:44:35.000Z","msg":"今年新年去左黃大仙求姻緣 中上籖<br />\n去日本求親姻緣籤 都係大吉<br />\n但我到依家仲係單身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9660db193e759c375f308cd361b3cb915edb4df8","tid":474333,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你去邊檔解籤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去雲姑 <br />\n解愛情 仲等緊準唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係雲姑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求左咩簽?<br />\n我之前都求左枝下下... 心諗以為死得 但雲姑都講到仲有機會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係等緊準唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊等邊充實自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我